| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1611 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9de5dc98-81de-5443-894e-c5ed8248e1e8"
